'''Procurement Development''' was a division of the [[Republic Defense Procurement Office/Legends|Republic Defense Procurement office]]. They were responsible for developing, testing and acquiring new technology and equipment for use by the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|GAR]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. One of the items they were developing was [[Dust]].

